---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kurzy pro borce | Reviews">
  <section class="max-w-[720px] mb-8">
    <h1
      class="font-display text-[clamp(36px,5vw,64px)] m-[8px_0_12px] text-navy"
    >
      Co rikaji borci
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Zažili to s nama a chtěj se podělit.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr))] gap-5">
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Adam V.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Byl jsem v životě na mnoha kurzech, ale že bych nechtěl, aby skončil, to
        se mi stalo poprvé.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Tomas O.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Dostal jsem darek Dokonalé aaaah a nic dalšího v životě nepotřebuju.
        Leda si zajít na kurz lamentování.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Michal R.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Uteklo to jak pěna z hrnku. Já snad půjdu znova.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Janek D.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Prakticke tipy, bezpecne prostredi a skvela parta. Doby je BOREC!
      </p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Ondra S.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Kurz me nakopnul a dal mi jasny plan na zlepseni. Žena si toho vsimla
        hned druhy den.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="bg-white/85 rounded-xl p-[22px] shadow-card relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:-bottom-[12px] after:left-6 after:w-0 after:h-0 after:border-l-[12px] after:border-l-transparent after:border-r-[12px] after:border-r-transparent after:border-t-[12px] after:border-t-white/85"
    >
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Radim M.</h2>
      <p class="italic text-sm">
        Lidi, co tomu rozumi a umi to predat bez nudy. Doufám, že přidají další
        kurzy!
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
